"AHHHHH!" as she is hit in the shoulder and side. She falls and 
cralws over to behind a tree.  She reaches for her gun and returns 
fire.
"What in the inferno is going? First Quickstrike, then DarkMouse, now 
this. I need a vacation."  She can't see who's firing the shots at 
her and Scorponok, but aims for where the shots are coming out from.
"Scorponok, you cover me, I'll take the mouse and bolt.  You have 
more fire power than I do."
